"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-30-chinese-olympic-athletes-dont-see-family-3-years-train-12-hours-a-day-21324042\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Germandiver Timo Barthel has revealed the huge sacrifices Chinese athletes have made in order to win gold at theOlympicsinParis, claiming that some of his rivals have not seen their families for three years.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 65, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.5870104147224744, \"rank\": 0.6901404002456969, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB's Tom Daley and Noah Williams produced six superb dives in the men's 10m synchro diving final\\u00a0on Mondaybut they were beaten to the gold medal byChina's duo of Lian Junjie and Hao Yang.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 209, \"end\": 216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9854741501558905, \"rank\": 0.014737501789066066, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9947023856173916e-41, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 233, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 376, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lian Junjie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_Junjie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley and Williams finished on 463.44 points but were blown away by an impressive display from Lian and Yang, who led the event from the first round and ended with 490.35 points.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 498, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\", \"score\": 0.8724513738767944, \"rank\": 0.12116834887074034, \"text\": \"Lian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Chinese did absolutely incredible today,' Daley said.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.5870104147224744, \"rank\": 0.6901404002456969, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They were on incredible form.\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every single one of their dives was flawless.'\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Barthel and his partner Jaden Eikermann represented Germany in the event and finished seventh overall with 364.41 points.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 794, \"end\": 801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}, {\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaden_Smith\", \"score\": 0.9999999947447122, \"rank\": 5.255272986015268e-09, \"text\": \"Jaden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaden_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jaden_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9905393158975634, \"rank\": 0.008640101182466586, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And speaking after the final, Barthel claims the strict regime of China's diving team plays a major role in their success at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}, {\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8121564267532068, \"rank\": 0.15595426142310126, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even with our best performance, we would have finished sixth today,' Barthel said.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And in Germany, a medal counts.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1150, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9905393158975634, \"rank\": 0.008640101182466586, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone talks and reports about it.\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And whether we finish fourth or seventh does not make much difference.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am proud of us and happy that we made it and qualified.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were in the final, we are in seventh place, and no one can take that away from us.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'That was the toughest competition this year.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Insane.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know if I have ever seen a 490 before.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Awesome competition.'\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking about the sacrifices made by China's divers ahead of the Olympics in Paris, Barthel said: 'They live in a boarding school, four to a room.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8121564267532068, \"rank\": 0.15595426142310126, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999997749, \"rank\": 2.2579972636372093e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They train for twelve hours.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not know anything other than diving.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not have a private life like we do where we go out with a girlfriend or partner, eat ice cream, go to restaurants, meet family.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes they do not see their family for three years.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'That is the difference between absolute world class and our performance today.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the question is also - do \\u200b\\u200byou want it that way?\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you want to have a life like that so that you can have gold?'\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Barthel also admits that the prize money on offer for winning gold is not enough to convince him to adopt the lifestyle of China's athletes.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2173, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}, {\"begin\": 2296, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8121564267532068, \"rank\": 0.15595426142310126, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I heard on the news that we get \\u20ac20,000 [\\u00a316,800] for a gold medal in Germany.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9905393158975634, \"rank\": 0.008640101182466586, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is it worth it?\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For \\u20ac20,000?\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That you put your whole life on hold?'\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Barthel said.\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2463, \"end\": 2470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"score\": 0.9999874173723032, \"rank\": 6.4001302768323675e-06, \"text\": \"Barthel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josy_Barthel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We already do that.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not live in Aachen anymore.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2516, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"score\": 0.9998329294294854, \"rank\": 0.00016652869204387348, \"text\": \"Aachen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aachen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I only do it for myself.\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, money does not play a role for us.'\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympics star screams in agony after suffering freak injury while celebrating medal win  ArrowMORE:Fans offer to pay TV star to stop showing off 'disgusting' injury  ArrowMORE:Two boxers cleared to fight as women in Olympics after being banned from World Championships  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 3121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3317, \"end\": 3323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202962604, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3621, \"entities\": []}]}"